OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782064079
OL,3,CGirl, nine, would have 'died very
OL,4,Cswiftly' after being stabbed, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA nine-year-old girl who was allegedly
OL,8,Ffatally stabbed by a teenage boy would
OL,9,Fhave died "very swiftly" from her
OL,10,Finjury, a pathologist has said.
OL,12,FAria Thorpe died after sustaining a
OL,13,Fknife wound to her chest at her home
OL,14,Fin Weston-super-Mare, North Somerset,
OL,15,Fon 15 December last year.
OL,17,FThe 16-year-old boy, who cannot be
OL,18,Fidentified due to his age, denies
OL,19,Fcharges of murder and manslaughter in
OL,20,Frelation to Aria's death.
OL,26,@qD@KOUqD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
