OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782064079
OL,3,CGirl, nine, would have 'died very
OL,4,Cswiftly' after being stabbed, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FBristol Crown Court has heard the boy
OL,8,Fran to a nearby train station after
OL,9,Fthe incident and told a group of
OL,10,Fchildren there that he had killed Aria
OL,11,Faccidentally.
OL,13,FDr Amanda Jeffery, a Home Office
OL,14,Fpathologist, told jurors that Aria
OL,15,Fdied as a result of a single stab
OL,16,Fwound to her chest, which went through
OL,17,Fher heart.
OL,19,F"Injuries to the heart of this nature
OL,20,Fcan result in sudden collapse and
OL,21,Fincapacitation," the pathologist said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782064079
OL,3,CGirl, nine, would have 'died very
OL,4,Cswiftly' after being stabbed, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"Some victims are capable of a short
OL,8,Fperiod of movement before they
OL,9,Fcollapse."
OL,11,FDr Jeffery said the distribution of
OL,12,Fblood at the scene suggested that Aria
OL,13,Fcollapsed "very quickly".
OL,15,F"Aria would have died very swiftly
OL,16,Ffrom an injury of this nature," she
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,19,FThe court heard Aria had a stab wound
OL,20,Fmeasuring 3.2cm wide and between 7.5
OL,21,Fand 8cm deep.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@JO]uD@KOUuD@XO]wD@AOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
