OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782064079
OL,3,CGirl, nine, would have 'died very
OL,4,Cswiftly' after being stabbed, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FJurors were shown a large kitchen
OL,8,Fknife with a green plastic handle and
OL,9,F21cm-long blade, which Dr Jeffery
OL,10,Fconfirmed was "capable of producing
OL,11,Fthe wound that was present".
OL,13,FShe said there were no other cuts to
OL,14,FAria's body and no defensive-type
OL,15,Finjuries.
OL,17,FThe court heard pathologists consider
OL,18,Fthe minimum level of force required to
OL,19,Fcause a wound, with the scale ranging
OL,20,Ffrom mild, moderate to severe.
OL,26,@rD@OOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
