OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782064079
OL,3,CGirl, nine, would have 'died very
OL,4,Cswiftly' after being stabbed, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FDr Jeffery told the jury that in this
OL,8,Fcase, the minimum level of force would
OL,9,Fbe "mild", but that greater force
OL,10,Fcould have been involved.
OL,12,FAria attended school on the day of her
OL,13,Fdeath and was collected from an after
OL,14,Fschool dance class by her mother, Tori
OL,15,FHull, at about 4.30pm.
OL,17,FThey went shopping for mini pizzas and
OL,18,Ftoppings, which they made together. Ms
OL,19,FHull left for an evening work shift
OL,20,Fshortly after, with Aria watching
OL,21,FYouTube videos on the television.
OL,26,@qD@DOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
