OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782064079
OL,3,CGirl, nine, would have 'died very
OL,4,Cswiftly' after being stabbed, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FFamily friend Ollie Sheppard, who was
OL,8,Fstaying temporarily at the house,
OL,9,Freturned there after work at about 6pm
OL,10,Fto find Aria on the floor of the
OL,11,Fliving room.
OL,13,FIn a 999 call read to the jury, Mr
OL,14,FSheppard told the call operator: "I
OL,15,Fhave literally just got home from
OL,16,Fwork, I've come through the door and
OL,17,Fcame into the living room.
OL,26,@vD@bOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
