OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782064079
OL,3,CGirl, nine, would have 'died very
OL,4,Cswiftly' after being stabbed, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"A little girl who lives here is on
OL,8,Fher front. I have turned her over and
OL,9,Fshe is covered in blood. There looks
OL,10,Flike a stab wound. Her face is going
OL,11,Fgrey. Oh my god."
OL,13,FPolice and paramedics attended the
OL,14,Fproperty, but Aria could not be saved
OL,15,Fand was pronounced dead at 6.58pm.
OL,17,FThe teenage defendant was arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of attempted murder after
OL,19,Fboarding a train at Worle railway
OL,20,Fstation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
