OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1782064079
OL,3,CGirl, nine, would have 'died very
OL,4,Cswiftly' after being stabbed, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FIn police interview, he gave a
OL,8,Fprepared statement describing how he
OL,9,Fhad stabbed Aria "in the chest".
OL,11,FHe later told the officers: "Just wish
OL,12,FI never did it".
OL,14,FThe trial, before Mrs Justice
OL,15,FO'Farrell, continues.
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@_O]sD@]OUtD@OO]
